SM6TwilightRogueBundle.name: Twilight Rogue
SM6TwilightRogueBundle.description: Outnumbered? No problem! Lycanroc does more damage when your opponent's Bench is full, so use Dusknoir to force your opponent to play more Basic Pokémon. Salazzle and Malamar pull more cards and more Energy—for more ways to win with the Twilight Rogue theme deck!
